{"tid":639111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：中國遊客在北韓遇車禍32人死亡團滅","createTime":"2018-04-23T08:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T12:24:38.000Z","uid":9031,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"779677d8fa509445c14edb2e6a6265448ad8e7d4","tid":639111,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"外交部表示，32名中國遊客在北韓黃海北道遇到嚴重交通意外死亡。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，車禍共造成36人死亡，32人是中國遊客，4人是北韓工作人員，另外有兩名中國公民重傷，情況極度危重。中國駐北韓大使館昨晚接到朝方通報這宗交通意外，相關詳情正在核實中。<br />\n<br />\n國家衛計委高度重視，連夜啟動衛生應急回應機制，從北京多間醫院抽調四名國家級醫療專家，並由衛計委衛生應急辦公室帶隊，組成國家醫療專家組，攜帶救治急需的器械及藥物，今日上午前往北韓，協助開展醫學救援工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392659-20180423.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392659-20180423.htm&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c03cc1a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1392659-20180423.htm&h=eba368ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1392659-20180423.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n今次唱國歌都冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a7d69129e41b836b7f9e49c461229f6f11eb93","tid":639111,"uid":77196,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"落地府唱國歌，叫閻王放人返陽間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40536948c89335d70073bfbdcd94d64e6dce5f41","tid":639111,"uid":47268,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:52:46.000Z","msg":"北韓做撚到野喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea06430a4e23c1c78017b7b05cdbb8587acce9b","tid":639111,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"來回地獄又折返人間<img src=\"/